                      <div class="FaqPage_faqItemAnswerCollapsibleInner__Ln6PE">
                        <div class="FaqPage_faqItemAnswer__HGfEd">If you have any technical issues, please contact our support team at<!-- --> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://OctoCPA.com/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#a2d1d7d2d2cdd0d6e2cdc1d6cdc1d2c38cc1cdcf"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="ee9d9b9e9e819c9aae818d9a818d9e8fc08d8183">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>. We will promptly process your request and make every effort to resolve the issue.</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="FaqPage_faqItem__inLMu" style="--mask-value:url(#:R59pusltrb:)"><svg class="FaqPage_faqItemBorderMask__PjztE" width="0" height="0">
                    <defs>
                      <mask id=":R59pusltrb:">
