                    <div class="FaqPage_faqItemAnswerCollapsible__Y1Ces">
                      <div class="FaqPage_faqItemAnswerCollapsibleInner__Ln6PE">
                        <div class="FaqPage_faqItemAnswer__HGfEd">We use modern tracking systems that allow us to accurately measure your traffic and conversions. Data update times may vary depending on the advertiser platform, all detailed information will be specified in the offer.</div>
