  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "ItemList",
      "itemListElement": [{
        "@type": "Review",
        "name": "Mikhail Sokolov",
        "reviewBody": "After several years of working with various affiliates, I switched to OctoCPA and have no regrets. High rates are not just a marketing gimmick, but a reality. I was especially pleased with the 5% bonus when I transferred money to OctoClick - it's an extra profit that I rarely find anywhere else. The analytics are really detailed, you can track every click and optimize campaigns on the fly. I recommend it to anyone who works seriously with ad traffic and wants a stable income.",
        "reviewRating": {
          "@type": "Rating",
          "ratingValue": 5,
          "bestRating": 5
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Review",
        "name": "Ivan Ivanov",
        "reviewBody": "After the OctoCPA presentation at Broconf 4 I decided to give it a try and it was a great solution. I started with small amounts of traffic, but after 2 weeks I realized I needed to scale up. Daytings offers have excellent conversion rates and payments come just in time. I would also like to mention the work of my personal manager - he always tells me what offers are trending and how best to set up a campaign. In six months I have increased my income by 2.5 times compared to my previous affiliate.",
        "reviewRating": {
          "@type": "Rating",
          "ratingValue": 5,
          "bestRating": 5
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Review",
        "name": "Alexey Morozov",
        "reviewBody": "I've been looking for an affiliate program that specializes in ads and pays decently. OctoCPA is exactly what an experienced arbitrageur needs. Flexible conditions, fast payouts and constantly updated offers. Yes, the interface is not perfect yet, but the functionality fully compensates for this shortcoming. Besides, the team is actively working on improvements. In 4 months of work we have never had any problems with withdrawing money, and this is worth a lot in our sphere.",
        "reviewRating": {
          "@type": "Rating",
          "ratingValue": 5,
          "bestRating": 5
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Review",
        "name": "Mia",
        "reviewBody": "First of all, thank you very much for giving us the opportunity to cooperate with us.\nI like that you can pay twice a week, and there’s only $100 payment threshold which is quite low. Also your response and approval always in time. I like working with you, hope we can make more volumes together.",
        "reviewRating": {
          "@type": "Rating",
          "ratingValue": 5,
          "bestRating": 5
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Review",
        "name": "Dmitry Volkov",
        "reviewBody": "I've been working with OctoCPA for 3 months since its launch and I'm very happy with the results. At first I was skeptical about new affiliates, but the history of connection with OctoClick convinced me to give it a try. The most important thing is that payments are stable and without delays, and the manager Alexey is always in touch and helps to optimize campaigns. Adalt offers really convert better than their competitors. I have already withdrawn over $3000 and continue to scale.",
        "reviewRating": {
          "@type": "Rating",
          "ratingValue": 5,
          "bestRating": 5
        }
      }]
    }
